title: Andy Warstar - 06/19/07 Melbourne, Oz
description:
Andy Warstar&#039;s first Melbourne performance at the Esplanade Hotel.

The performance went well, even though the sound guy miked Andy&#039;s

fretboard instead of the f-hole on the guitar. Andy didn&#039;t know the

middle of the fretboard was hitting the mike, creating a few pops

(that have been minimized in the mastering).

The dickhead manager pulled Andy off the stage five minutes early, citing

the popping noise as the reason, as Andy&#039;s fault, calling Andy "abrasive".

What a stupid motherfucking fuck. The reality is that the sound guy is

an inexperienced moron, and Andy Warstar is great regardless.
